These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
House: victorian, futuristic
City: new-york, paris
2 different games are played: backgammon, bridge
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person who growsazalea is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the victorian house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Birthday    | april   | december        |
| House   | victorian    | futuristic |
| City     | paris  | new-york       |
| Game     | backgammon   | bridge         |
| Flower   | azalea | aconite      |

