.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, january
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, mechanic
2 different games are played: canasta, scrabble
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the mechanic##8
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Flower         | sunflower   | daffodil |
| Color   | blood-red  | orange     |
| Birthday   | september  | january        |
| Job           | entrepreneur     | mechanic       |
| Game         | canasta | scrabble     |

